name: Fixed Gear Girl
description:
ARAINA Retro T-Shirts 

ARAINA is an up and coming t-shirt brand selling Retro Inspired Graffic T-Shirts, designed for people who want to stand out from the crowd.

We have a limited number of each style of our tees so when they are gone they are gone!

SIZE GUIDE

MEDIUM: Chest 19 inches (armpit to armpit)

              Length 28 inches (mid shoulder to bottom hem)

LARGE:   Chest 20 inches (armpit to armpit)

              Length 29 inches (mid shoulder to bottom hem)

100% Cotton
